---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Muhammad Fiaz, a full-stack developer and open-source contributor from Madurai, India.
        <br />
        My primary tools of choice include JavaScript, React, Node.js, Astro, Svelte, FastAPI, Python, and AI/ML Technologies.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about AI, machine learning, building developer tools, and solving real-world problems through software. In my free time, I enjoy exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source, and experimenting with new ideas.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      While I have a preferred set of tools, I always choose the best one for the job, ensuring I deliver efficient, scalable, and reliable solutions. My goal is to continually learn and grow as a developer.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
